The [[UCL Faculty of Laws|Faculty of Laws]] at [[University College London]] occupies Bentham House, next to the main UCL campus.&lt;ref name=&quot;UCL8&quot; /&gt;

Bentham's name was adopted by the Australian [[Legal financing|litigation funder]] IMF Limited to become Bentham IMF Limited on 28 November 2013, in recognition of Bentham being &quot;among the first to support the utility of litigation funding&quot;.&lt;ref name=&quot;imf.com.au&quot; /&gt;

